Download BgInfo from here: https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/sysinternals/downloads/bginfo

The extract the files and open the 64bit version 

Set whatever you like (cpu, ram, network speed, adapters,etc)

Finally set up a cool font (like Gill Sans MT at size 9) and done!

You can also move the position, add colors and even set other commadns you like
